com.skratchdot.riff.wav

Interface ChunkDataListTypeLabeledText

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Chunk, ChunkDataListType
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChunkDataListTypeLabeledTextImpl

    public interface ChunkDataListTypeLabeledText
extends ChunkDataListType
    A representation of the model object 'Chunk Data List Type Labeled Text'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Sample Length
    • Purpose ID
    • Country
    • Language
    • Dialect
    • Code Page

    See Also:
    WavPackage.getChunkDataListTypeLabeledText()
